    description: Mattermost
    action: Message us
  - icon: inbox
    link: http://lists.zeus.ugent.be/mailman/listinfo/leden
    description: Mailinglist
    action: Keep up to date
  - icon: github
    link: https://github.com/ZeusWPI/
    description: GitHub
